# QuadRenderSystem  (sbx)

## Purpose
Render bridge for world-space quads: sole adder of DrawQuadInFrameEvent. Each frame it emits one
in-frame draw event per QuadComponent, copying the quad's transform, colour, origin and texture
id. A null texture id yields a flat colour quad; a set texture id yields a textured quad
(Renderer2DSystem then batches and draws them).

## Input Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| QuadComponent | read | One draw event emitted per quad |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| DrawQuadInFrameEvent | add (inframe) | One per QuadComponent; consumed by Renderer2DSystem this frame |
